  "description": "PROBE iEEG is a multimodal dataset comprising stereoelectroencephalography (sEEG) intracranial recordings from patients undergoing epilepsy surgery evaluation, along with structural MRI scans acquired before and after surgical intervention. The dataset includes raw electrophysiological data collected during clinical monitoring and structural neuroimaging data suitable for investigating neural dynamics during epilepsy surgery evaluation.",
